metadata.description:
WHERE'S MY STUFF?
1) If you recently made a purchase using crypto, please give it up to 48 hours for the transaction to settle, although it usually takes less than an hour. 
2) Depending on which wallet you use, you may need to change your settings before new NFT assets become visible. 
3) If you see your NFT in the wallet but are having trouble downloading your assets, type the following shorturl web address into a browser and use the first 6 digits of the crypto wallet you used to make the purchase as your password: 

TYPE IN BROWSER:   shorturl.at/grW79

Password is the first 6 digits of your wallet address, all lowercase.

This Limited Edition DuckDown T3 Original Blue Sneaker NFT consists of 1 JPG image, 1 3D file, and 1 3DAR Augmented Reality file for the Digital Duck Down T3 Original Blue Sneaker, featuring the Classic Duck Down running man logo. The value of this digital T3 sneaker NFT is $35 USD which breaks down as: $5 USD  JPG image and $30 USD per 3D assets. Also included in this NFT are the following bonus assets: 1 Animated video featuring the classic blue T3 digital sneaker, 1 New Music MP3 titled Come Back Like This by Buckshot BDI featuring Swan Gotti, and 1 New Music Video MP4 titled Come Back Like This by Buckshot BDI featuring Swan Gotti, valued as follows: $5 T3 classic blue sneaker animation video, $10 Music MP3, and $10 Music Video MP4. The total value of this limited edition NFT is $60 USD. 

Be sure to check DuckdownNFTs.com often with your proof of purchase of this NFT to get various discounts and other special offers available only to owners of this NFT.
